# How To Know How Essential Oils Interact With Drugs

Welcome! I’m Elizabeth Ashley—UK Director for the National Association for Holistic Aromatherapy (NAHA), author of *The Secret Healer Aromatherapy Manuals*, and a clinical aromatherapist with over 30 years of experience.

In this video, I explain how you can understand **essential oil interactions with pharmaceutical drugs**, and how to approach blending safely when medications are involved.

