## 📝 What You’ll Learn in This Video

✅ **How essential oils can interact with medications** via liver enzymes  
✅ **Which medications are more susceptible to interaction risks**  
✅ **Trusted places to research essential oil safety** before blending  
✅ **Why AI and internet lists can be misleading or unsafe**  
✅ **Practical steps to protect yourself and your clients** when blending with medications in mind

This guide will help you understand how to **use essential oils responsibly**, respecting potential drug interactions while still enjoying the benefits of aromatherapy.

